            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>Thai green curry paste</strong> to the pan with the chicken and cook for 2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>creamed coconut</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>, add your<strong> fish sauce</strong> with your<strong> lime leaf[ves]</strong>, the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lime[s]</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>– this is your <strong>fragrant stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
