          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chilli </strong>finely</p>",
      "order": 7,
