    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>fragrant Thai green free range chicken curry</strong> over the <strong>lemongrass rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!), <strong>coriander leaves</strong> and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
